text: StarDog and TurboCat is a 2019 British computer animated comic science fiction movie produced by Red Star 3D for Kaleidoscope Film Distribution. It stars Nick Frost, Luke Evans, Gemma Arterton, Bill Nighy, Ben Bailey Smith, Charli D'Amelio and Cory English.
